!help:
`/help`

Provides total list of commands with small description
!helpme:
`/helpme` <!command>

Provides full description and argument requirements of command
!setname:
`/setname` <username>

**Requirements:**

__<username>:__
min legth - 3 symbols
max legth - 12 symbols

Can be used to name change
*__Creates session for new users__
!setpass:
`/setpass` <password>

**Requirements:**

__<password>:__
min legth - 3 symbols
max legth - 64 symbols

Can be used to password change
!login:
`/login` <username> <password>

**Requirements:**

__<username>:__
The username of profile
__<password>:__
The password of profile

Can be used to getting username from other profile
!profile:
`/profile`

Provides your profile info
*__ Don't forward to other users__
!newroom:
`/newroom` <room name> <password> <type>

**Requirements:**

__<room name>:__
Public name of your room
__<password>:__
min legth - 6 symbols
max legth - 12 symbols
__<type>:__
open or private

Can be used to room creation
!delroom:
`/delroom` <room name> <password>

Can be used for room delete
*__Only creator can delete room__
!connect:
`/connect` <room name> <password>

**Requirements:**

__<password>:__
Only when connecting to private room

Can be used to connect to the room
*__To send message, please reply to Chat History you're connected__
!disconnect:
`/disconnect`

Can be used to disconnect from room
